Class TypeWrapper

java.lang.Object
  thewebsemantic.TypeWrapper

public class TypeWrapper
extends java.lang.Object

Retrieves annotation information as well as other type related operations on Classes. Keeps cached versions to minimize introspection work.

uri

public java.lang.String uri(java.beans.PropertyDescriptor pd)
returns a URI pointing to the rdf property resource. If the property descriptor is annotated with an explicit uri, then we'll use the URI specified in the annotation, otherwise a URI is created using the following naming pattern.

If the property name is "age" and the namespace for this type is http://example.org/, the resulting URI will be http://example.org/hasAge.
